title: Shiva
subTitle: When a police inspector manages to capture a member of a human trafficking ring, the gang leader vows to take revenge. He relentlessly hunts for the officer with an intention to kill him.

title: Akritagya
subTitle: Trishna's maternal uncle kills her father in order to seek the latter's property. Later, Trishna strives to take revenge, however, dark secrets are revealed.

title: Debdas
subTitle: Debdas resorts to drinking after he is unable to marry the love of his life, Paro. However, as his situation worsens, he decides to pay her a visit before he dies.

title: Dui Prithibi
subTitle: A rich man falls in love with an idealistic medical student. However, when circumstances force them apart, he learns the true meaning and value of love.

title: Satrur Muqubila
subTitle: Awbhoy, a dedicated police officer, develops a deep romantic interest in a young woman attending a job interview while undergoing training.

title: Mahaan
subTitle: Ajit adopts Chandu, who later falls for a girl named Mala. Trouble arises for Chandu when Mala's father turns out to be Ajit's boss.

title: Bandhan

title: Kencho Khunrte Keute
subTitle: Gyanoda loses his son and daughter-in-law, leaving his granddaughter Parama as a spoilt child. To discipline her, he leaves a will which requires her to marry to gain full inheritance access.

title: Premer Kahini
subTitle: Akash falls in love with Barsha but loses contact with her due to unforeseeable circumstances. While attending a marriage ceremony, he is shocked to realise that the bride is none other than Barsha.

title: Indrajit
subTitle: Indrajit is an honest police officer who punishes Raja, an MLA's son, for raping a girl. The MLA then kidnaps the former's son and demands Raja's release.

title: Satyanweshi
